fields.Title: Physical Instrument: "You didn't shut him down. Your fat..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You didn't shut him down. Your fat fist didn't meet its target. Instead, it pulled you down with it.
fields.Sequence: SetTriggerAnimation(Cuno,CunoPunchFail); SetTriggerAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PunchCunoF, false, true); HideActualHeld(); BanishInterface(true); BanishInterface(false)@7; LuaRun(DamageEndurance(1))@7; Release();

fields.Title: Smoker on the Balcony: "I would often go there / To the tin..."
fields.Dialogue Text:
I would often go there / To the tiny church there / The smallest church in Saint-Saëns / Though it once was larger

How the rill may rest there / Down through the mist there / Toward the seven sisters / Toward those pale cliffs there

I would often stay there / In there tiny yard there / I have been so glad here / Looking forward to the past here

But now you are alone /None of this matters at all

fields.Title: Jump to: [Kim Kitsuragi: ""I will escort you to the motor car..."]
Smoker on the Balcony: "[Leave] I'm done."
Physical Instrument: "Thump! That blow connects surprisin..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Thump! That blow connects surprisingly well. Your knuckles tingle.
fields.Sequence: SetTriggerAnimation(Cuno,CunoPunchSuccess)@4.1; SetTriggerAnimation(Tequila Sunset, PunchCunoS); HideActualHeld(); BanishInterface(true); BanishInterface(false)@7; Release();
